131
00:22:16,628 --> 00:22:21,133
We also need Capt. Campbell's
personal and medical records.

132
00:22:21,341 --> 00:22:25,721
- I already did that.
- Thank you.

133
00:22:25,929 --> 00:22:31,143
- Sarah Sunhill, Paul Brenner.
- And book Sgt. Dalbert Elkins.

134
00:22:31,351 --> 00:22:34,354
He's the one
who started the arms deal.

135
00:22:36,565 --> 00:22:40,194
She walked barefoot from here
to where she died.

136
00:22:40,527 --> 00:22:44,156
There's smudge marks on her heels
and the asphalt. Where did she live?

137
00:22:44,364 --> 00:22:48,327
