without a civilian search warrant.

141
00:23:03,050 --> 00:23:06,803
You need civilian authority.

142
00:23:07,012 --> 00:23:12,935
- We protect Brenner from himself.
- Does she have family here?

143
00:23:13,143 --> 00:23:16,897
- Of course.
- I suggest you notify them.

144
00:23:23,487 --> 00:23:27,741
- You're kidding, right?
