We'll always have Brussels.

155
00:24:35,100 --> 00:24:38,437
- Where?
- The capital of Belgium.

156
00:24:40,022 --> 00:24:41,565
Why?

157
00:24:41,773 --> 00:24:46,987
Why is it the capital,
or why will we always have it?

158
00:24:48,155 --> 00:24:51,492
