- Very sorry for your loss, sir.

171
00:26:24,501 --> 00:26:28,755
Thank you.
Please, be seated.

172
00:26:36,388 --> 00:26:41,476
First, I want you to know
you have my full co-operation -

173
00:26:41,685 --> 00:26:45,230
