190
00:28:24,496 --> 00:28:28,792
If there's anything else
we can do for you at this time ...

191
00:28:29,835 --> 00:28:32,129
Just ...

192
00:28:34,631 --> 00:28:39,303
- Just find the son of a bitch.
- Yes, sir.

193
00:28:44,933 --> 00:28:47,436
Sir ...

194
00:28:47,644 --> 00:28:53,901
When I enlisted I was under-age.
They sent me straight to Vietnam.

195
00:28:54,234 --> 00:28:58,405
You were my commander.
You were a captain.

196
00:28:58,614 --> 00:29:02,159
And I was so scared.

197
00:29:02,367 --> 00:29:07,789
One day, when I was on watch,
you came by and you saw the fear.

198
00:29:07,998 --> 00:29:12,794
You said, ''Where are you from?''
I said, ''Boston.''

199
00:29:13,003 --> 00:29:16,965
