208
00:30:15,023 --> 00:30:21,071
We don't like our personnel arrested
by outsiders without our knowing.

209
00:30:21,405 --> 00:30:23,991
There are three ways
of doing things:

210
00:30:24,199 --> 00:30:28,996
The right way, the wrong way
and the army way.

211
00:30:29,204 --> 00:30:34,543
See that, in doing it your way,
you don't forget about the army way.

212
00:30:59,234 --> 00:31:03,947
<i>Our job at Psy Ops is to blunt
the enemy's will to fight.</i>

213
00:31:04,156 --> 00:31:08,410
<i>You must know
the hablts of the enemy, -</i>

214
00:31:08,619 --> 00:31:11,955
