- Colonel Robert Moore.

222
00:31:46,907 --> 00:31:50,661
Capt. Campbell's commanding officer.
And you are ..?

223
00:31:50,869 --> 00:31:56,708
Criminal lnvestigation Division.
Sunhill and Brenner.

224
00:31:58,168 --> 00:32:04,216
